{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 44,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الدُّخَانِ",
    "englishName": "Ad-Dukhaan",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Smoke",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 59,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4415,
        "text": "HaMeem",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4416,
        "text": "By the Clear Book",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4417,
        "text": "that We sent down during a Blessed Night. We are ever warning.",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4418,
        "text": "In it every wise matter is determined",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4419,
        "text": "an order from Us. We are ever sending.",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4420,
        "text": "A Mercy from your Lord, He is the Hearer, the Knower.",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4421,
        "text": "Lord of the heavens and the earth and all that is between them, if you are certain (of your faith).",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4422,
        "text": "There is no god except He. He revives and causes to die. (He is) your Lord and the Lord of your fathers, the ancients.",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4423,
        "text": "Yet they are in doubt, playing.",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4424,
        "text": "Watch for the Day when the heaven will bring clear smoke,",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4425,
        "text": "engulfing the people; this will be a painful punishment.",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4426,
        "text": "'Our Lord, remove this punishment from us, we are believers'",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4427,
        "text": "But how will they avail themselves of the Reminder, when a clear Messenger had already come to them",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4428,
        "text": "but then they turned away from him, saying: 'He is tutored, mad'",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4429,
        "text": "We are removing the punishment a little, but you revert.",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4430,
        "text": "But on that Day We will assault them most mightily, and then We shall revenge!",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 198,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4431,
        "text": "We tried Pharaoh's nation before them. A noble Messenger came to them,",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4432,
        "text": "(saying:) 'Be obedient to me O worshipers of Allah. I am your honest Messenger.",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 496,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4433,
        "text": "Do not rise up against Allah, I come to you with clear authority.",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4434,
        "text": "I take refuge with my Lord and your Lord lest you stone me.",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4435,
        "text": "And if you do not believe me, then leave me'",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4436,
        "text": "Then he supplicated to his Lord saying: 'These are sinful people'",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4437,
        "text": "(His Lord answered): 'Set out with My worshipers in the night, for you will surely be followed.",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4438,
        "text": "Then leave the sea calm they are an army that will be drowned.",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4439,
        "text": "How many gardens and fountains did they leave behind,",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4440,
        "text": "and sown fields, fine sitting places,",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4441,
        "text": "and good things in which they took delight.",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4442,
        "text": "As such (it was). And We made other people inherit them.",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4443,
        "text": "Neither heaven nor earth shed tears for them; nor were they respited,",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 431,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4444,
        "text": "and We saved the Children of Israel from a humiliating punishment",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4445,
        "text": "from Pharaoh, who ranked high in sin,",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4446,
        "text": "and We chose them, out of a knowledge above the nations (of their time).",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4447,
        "text": "And gave signs to them in which there was a clear trial.",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4448,
        "text": "Yet these say:",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4449,
        "text": "'There is nothing except the first death, we shall never be revived.",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4450,
        "text": "Bring us our fathers, if what you say is true'",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4451,
        "text": "Are they better or the people of Tubba' and those who were before them whom We destroyed? Indeed they were sinners.",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4452,
        "text": "It was not in play that We created the heavens and the earth and all that is between them.",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4453,
        "text": "We created them in nothing else except the truth. But most do not know.",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 497,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4454,
        "text": "The Day of Decision is the appointed time for all.",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4455,
        "text": "On that Day no cousin shall help his cousin and they shall not be helped",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4456,
        "text": "except those on whom Allah will have mercy. He is the Almighty, the Most Merciful.",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 432,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4457,
        "text": "The food of the Zakkum tree",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4458,
        "text": "shall be the food of the guilty sinners.",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4459,
        "text": "Like molten copper boiling in the belly",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4460,
        "text": "as the boiling of the hot water.",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4461,
        "text": "'Seize him and drag him into the center of Hell.",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4462,
        "text": "Then pour the punishment of boiling water over his head,",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4463,
        "text": "(Saying): 'Taste, surely you are the mighty and noble!",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4464,
        "text": "This is that which you doubted'",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4465,
        "text": "Indeed, for those who feared (Allah) is a secure place",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4466,
        "text": "amidst gardens and fountains,",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4467,
        "text": "dressed in silks and brocade, set face to face.",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4468,
        "text": "As such, We shall wed them to wideeyed houris (the virgins of Paradise).",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4469,
        "text": "There in security, they will call for every kind of fruit.",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4470,
        "text": "There they shall not taste death, except the first death, and He will shield them from the punishment of Hell,",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4471,
        "text": "as a bounty from your Lord. That will be the mighty triumph.",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4472,
        "text": "We have now made it easy on your tongue, in order that they remember.",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4473,
        "text": "So be watchful, they too are watching.",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 25,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 498,
        "ruku": 433,
        "hizbQuarter": 199,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
